Problem: In companies, due to absence of tagging system, it is hard to find necessary document after long period of time.
Solution: Make document classication system.

Dataset:
    fetch_20newsgroups (total ~17K):
        SciKit-Learn Database
    BBC full text classification (total ~2200):
        https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/shivamkushwaha/bbc-full-text-document-classification
